# TASK-008 完成摘要

## 实现内容

### 1. ProjectService (`lib/projects/project-service.ts`)
- `createProject(userId, title, slug)`：创建项目，分配 `storage_prefix`，默认 draft 状态
- `deleteProject(userId, projectId)`：Q6 软删流程（先软删 DB → 再删 R2 对象 → `storage_delete_pending` 补偿）
- `getProjectsForDashboard(userId)`：返回用户所有项目，五态入口映射
- `getProjectDetail(userId, projectId)`：元数据不含正文，越权访问通过 `getProjectForUser` 拒绝

### 2. 五态路由映射
| 状态 | 路由 |
|------|------|
| draft | `/projects/[projectId]/wizard` |
| planning | `/projects/[projectId]/planning` |
| writing | `/projects/[projectId]/write` |
| validating | `/projects/[projectId]/complete` |
| completed | `/projects/[projectId]/read` |

### 3. Server Actions (`app/actions/projects.ts`)
- `createProject(input)`：创建项目并返回跳转 URL
- `deleteProject(projectId)`：软删处理
- `getProjectsDashboard()`：获取仪表盘列表
- `getProjectDetail(projectId)`：获取项目详情
- `getWritingProgressInfo(projectId)`：获取创作进度信息

### 4. 仪表盘页面 (`app/[locale]/(app)/dashboard/page.tsx`)
- 列表卡片按状态跳转正确路由
- 新建作品按钮 → `/projects/new`
- 进度条展示（writing/validating 状态）
- 空状态引导

